#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "2,000 parents<br/> brought their kid to our nursery."
msgstr "2.000 forældre<br/> har valgt vores vuggestue til deres barn."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid "A little place <br/>of paradise"
msgstr "Et lille stykke <br/>paradis"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "About us"
msgstr "Om os"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "Aktiviteter"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"All activities are planned to meet each child’s individual needs. This "
"approach will help your child to develop to the best of their ability."
msgstr ""
"Alle aktiviteter planlægges på en sådan måde, at hvert barns individuelle "
"behov imødekommes. Denne tilgang hjælper dit barn med at udvikle sig bedst "
"muligt."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "Kontakt os"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Entrust us with your children and go to work with peace of mind"
msgstr "Overlad dine børn til os, og gå trygt på arbejde"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Events"
msgstr "Arrangementer"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid "For every kid"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_cover
msgid "Kiddo Nursery"
msgstr "Kiddo-børnehave"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_picture
msgid "Letting each child explore and grow at their own pace"
msgstr "Hvert barn udvikler sig og vokser i sit eget tempo"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid "Open-door policy"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Our aim is to make the early years of your child’s life as enjoyable, "
"rewarding and positive as possible."
msgstr ""
"Vores mål er at gøre de første år i dit barns liv så underholdende, "
"behagelige og positive som muligt."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid "Our mission"
msgstr "Vores mission"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_picture
msgid ""
"Our qualified staff ensure that each childs' needs are always recognised and"
" fulfilled."
msgstr ""
"Vores kvalificerede personale sørger for, at hvert barns behov altid bliver "
"erkendt og opfyldt."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Our team"
msgstr "Vores team"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Our team is composed of experienced nursery nurses."
msgstr "Vores team består af erfarne børnehavepædagoger."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Playground"
msgstr "Legeplads"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_cover
msgid ""
"The countryside nursery since 2002.<br/>\n"
"        A truly unique service in a highly secure and tranquil setting."
msgstr ""
"Børnehaven på landet siden 2002.<br/>\n"
"        En virkelig enestående service i et yderst sikkert og roligt miljø."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_kiddo.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Designværktøjer"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid ""
"They will propose to your children educational activities, playful, varied "
"and adapted to the stage of development."
msgstr ""
"De vil foreslå jeres børn pædagogiske aktiviteter, der er legende, "
"afvekslende og tilpasset deres udviklingsniveau."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid ""
"This is a simple hero unit, a simple jumbotron-style component for calling "
"extra attention to featured content or information."
msgstr ""
"Dette er en simpel hero-enhed i fuldskærmsstil, designet til at fremhæve "
"udvalgt indhold eller information og tiltrække ekstra opmærksomhed."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_picture
msgid ""
"Through stimulating and fun activities, our aim<br/>\n"
"        is to promote all areas of a childs' development."
msgstr ""
"Vores mål er gennem stimulerende og underholdende aktiviteter<br/>\n"
"        at fremme alle områder af børns udvikling."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Visit us"
msgstr "Besøg os"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"You are welcome to come and see the nursery and meet the team at any time "
"convenient to you."
msgstr ""
"Du er altid velkommen til at besøge vores børnehave og møde personalet, når "
"det passer dig."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/theme_kiddo/static/src/js/tour.js:0
#, python-format
msgid "width"
msgstr "bredde"
